      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "A wrong solution. Logical error. If the inner class (e.g. ZShape) requires any field to be set, in the outer class&#39;s constructor you must get it! public  Shape(String field1_innerClass, int field2_innerClass...){zShape = new ZShape(String field1_innerClass, int field2_innerClass...)...}}"
